                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6531" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1030</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8939 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新疆中联：蓄力谋转型，税惠指方向</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Xinjiang Zhonglian: saving energy for transformation, tax benefits pointing to the direction</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李莉，许晴，刘宁，庞敏，姬阿明，戴双红，赵书艺，王雪，刘媛媛</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新疆大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新疆中联软件有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新疆中联；税收优惠政策；企业转型；医疗信息化；2022百优案例；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Xinjiang Zhonglian; Preferential tax policy; Enterprise transformation;  Medical informatization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，软件行业受到国家的高度重视和国家税收政策的重点支持，不断提升研发能力是软件企业未来发展的方向。本案例研究对象新疆中联是一家从事医疗信息化的企业。2020年以来，尽管受疫情影响，但新疆中联抓住机遇、借力国家税收优惠政策，从一家软件代理商转型为新疆地区最大的医疗软件开发与集成服务商，将目光聚焦在集成化数字医疗服务领域。本案例描述了新疆中联从管理和业务两个口径出发苦练内功，通过优化内部管理——培训助力、数字赋能、业财融合、分工规范管理；改变业务口径——“两改”、“三调”等措施，更充分享受税收优惠政策，从而突破了企业面临的市场需求变化快、要求高，可持续发展的价值实现受阻以及疫情下公司资金链运转困难等“内忧外患”的诸多困境，成功实现企业高新技术转型。本案例旨在引导学生了解掌握软件行业税收优惠政策，深度思考国家税收政策对企业进行科技转型的重要支撑作用以及软件企业在落实税收优惠政策的过程中遇到的困难及解决办法。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> In recent years, the software industry has received high attention from the state and key support from the national tax policy, and continuous improvement of R&amp;D capability is the direction of future development of software enterprises. Xinjiang Zhonglian, the subject of this case study, is an enterprise engaged in medical informatization. since 2020, despite the impact of the epidemic, Xinjiang Zhonglian has seized the opportunity to transform from a software agent to the largest medical software development and integration service provider in Xinjiang, focusing on the field of integrated digital medical services by taking advantage of the national tax incentives. This case describes Xinjiang Zhonglian&#39;s hard practice of internal strength from both management and business calibers, through optimizing internal management - booster, digital empowerment, industry and financial integration, division of labor and standardized management; changing business calibers - &quot;two changes &quot;, &quot;three adjustments&quot; and other measures, more fully enjoy the preferential tax policies, so as to break through the rapid changes in market demand, high requirements, sustainable development of the value of the company to achieve hindered and the epidemic under the company&#39;s capital chain running difficulties and other &quot;internal and external problems &quot;This case aims at guiding students to understand how to use the software and how to use it. This case aims to guide students to understand and grasp the tax preferential policies of the software industry, to think deeply about the important role of national tax policies in supporting the transformation of enterprises into science and technology and the difficulties and solutions encountered by software enterprises in the process of implementing tax preferential policies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《宏观经济政策分析与财务决策》、《税务会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新疆中联转型，高质量发展的含义；PEST分析工具；SWOT分析工具；增值税、所得税的涵义；技术开发费的税前扣除；研究阶段的定义；开发阶段的定义；研发费用加计扣除政策；协同治理理论；业财融涵合义</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
